'''GLAM'''是[[美術館|美術館]]（galleries）、[[圖書館|圖書館]]（libraries）、[[檔案|檔案館]]（archives）及[[博物館|博物館]]（museums）組合而成的[[首字母縮略字|首字母縮略字]]<ref>Australian Society of Archivists, [https://web.archive.org/web/20030801224434/http://www.archivists.org.au/events/conf2003/ Australian Society of Archivists Annual Conference - GLAM], 17–20 September 2003, Hilton, Adelaide.[https://books.google.com/books/about/Glam.html?id=fRwMRAAACAAJ]</ref><ref name="CC Wiki">{{cite web|url=http://wiki.creativecommons.org/GLAM|title=GLAM - CC Wiki|publisher=Creative Commons|accessdate=29 October 2011|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402100143/https://wiki.creativecommons.org/GLAM|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，是指其宗旨是幫助大眾[[獲取知識|獲取知識]]的{{le|文化組織|cultural institutions}}。

也有使用過其他的略縮字，例如只包括圖書館、檔案館及博物館的'''LAM'''（其中沒有包括美術館，美術館可以視為是博物館的子集合，而且美術館galleries也容易和商業買賣藝術作品的商業畫廊混淆）<ref>{{cite web |author=BibSI |url=http://bibsi.cms.si.umich.edu/node/212 |title=On the LAM: Library, Archive, and Museum Collections in the Creation and Maintenance of Knowledge Communities | BibSI |publisher=Bibsi.cms.si.umich.edu |date= |accessdate=2012-04-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305191920/http://bibsi.cms.si.umich.edu/node/212 |archivedate=2014-03-05 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://lam.alaska.gov/ |title=Internet Archive Wayback Machine |publisher=Web.archive.org |date=2008-12-22 |accessdate=2012-04-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20090501071432/http%3A//lam%2Ealaska%2Egov/ |archivedate=2009-05-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=LAM DNA August 4, 2005 by Jim |url=http://hangingtogether.org/?p=15 |title=Blog Archive » LAM DNA |publisher=hangingtogether.org |date=2005-08-04 |accessdate=2012-04-05 |archive-date=2013-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511133820/http://hangingtogether.org/?p=15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，另外有一種略縮字是GLAMR，加上了文件中心（Records）<ref>{{cite web|title=2017 Conference - Australian Society of Archivists|url=https://www.archivists.org.au/learning-publications/2017-conference|website=www.archivists.org.au|accessdate=19 June 2017|archive-date=2018-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911130337/https://www.archivists.org.au/learning-publications/2017-conference|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。一般來說，GLAM是指公眾資助，收集[[文化遗产|文化遗产]]的機構。

